public class string {
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        String str="java programming";
        System.out.println("the string is"+str+",");
        System.out.println("length of the string is "+str.length());
        System.out.println("Character at second and fourth position is"+str.charAt(1)+","+str.charAt(3));
        System.out.println("the hub string using start index only is"+str.substring(5));
        System.out.println("the hub string using start index only is"+str.substring((int) 0.4));
    }
}

output
..............
length of the string is 16
Character at second and fourth position isa,a
the hub string using start index only isprogramming
the hub string using start index only isjava programming

Process finished with exit code 0
